			    CALCULATE(
			        [Total Gross Revenue],
			        DATEADD('gold dim_date'[full_date], -1, MONTH)
			    )
			RETURN
			    DIVIDE(_CM - _PM, _PM)
			```
		displayFolder: Functionality
		lineageTag: 524d8061-a6c5-4435-87d1-5d8cb37d6428

		annotation PBI_FormatHint = {"isGeneralNumber":true}

